HEADWORD: Misapply
<hw>Mis`ap*ply"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. &
p. p.</pos> <conjf>Misapplied</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb.
n.</pos> <conjf>Misapplying</conjf>.]</vmorph> <def>To apply wrongly; to
